OL,3,CBarbecue warning after benches and
OL,4,Cbranches burnt at Jersey reservoir
OL,6,FJersey Water has warned islanders
OL,7,Fabout the dangers of lighting
OL,8,Fbarbecues in open countryside after
OL,9,Fpicnic benches and tree branches were
OL,10,Fleft burnt at Val de la Mare Reservoir.
OL,12,FThe company says that while the damage
OL,13,Fwas not severe, it could have been a
OL,14,Flot worse if the fire had got out of
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,FMark Bowden, Jersey Water's Asset
OL,18,FManager, told ITV News: "It just
OL,19,Fpresents a real risk of fires which
OL,20,Fcan spread and cause real devastation
OL,21,Facross the land.
