OL,3,CBarbecue warning after benches and
OL,4,Cbranches burnt at Jersey reservoir
OL,6,FSpeaking about the impact of the
OL,7,Fdamage, Mr Bowden said: "It just adds
OL,8,Fto the overall degradation of the
OL,9,Farea. The last thing we want is for
OL,10,Fthis place to get a reputation for
OL,11,Fbeing a place where people can have
OL,12,Ffires so we really need to stamp it
OL,13,Fout and make sure that this site is
OL,14,Flooked after."
OL,16,FJohn Michel from environmental charity
OL,17,FJersey Trees for Life also spoke about
OL,18,Fthe dangers of lighting fires in the
OL,19,Fsummer.
