OL,6,FHe said: "It's (fire) dangerous
OL,7,Fanytime it's dry but it's particularly
OL,8,Fdangerous at this time of year when
OL,9,Fthe sun's been out.
OL,11,FWhen asked what sort of impact a
OL,12,Flarger fire could have on the natural
OL,13,Fhabitats around the reservoir, Mr
OL,14,FMichel said: "It's not something you
OL,15,Flike to think about too much.
OL,16,FObviously around here we've got plenty
OL,17,Fof non-native trees and saplings
OL,18,Faround which we'd be deeply concerned
OL,19,Fabout because they were specially
OL,20,Fselected and sourced as well.
